descriptor.name: Apple iPhone 15 (128 GB) - Black
descriptor.short_desc: Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities — so you don’t miss them while you’re doing something else
descriptor.long_desc:
DYNAMIC ISLAND COMES TO IPHONE 15 — Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities — so you don’t miss them while you’re doing something else. You can see who’s calling, track your next ride, check your flight status, and so much more.
INNOVATIVE DESIGN — iPhone 15 features a durable color-infused glass and aluminum design. It’s splash, water, and dust resistant. The Ceramic Shield front is tougher than any smartphone glass. And the 6.1" Super Retina XDR display is up to 2x brighter in the sun compared to iPhone 14.
48MP MAIN CAMERA WITH 2X TELEPHOTO — The 48MP Main camera shoots in super-high resolution. So it’s easier than ever to take standout photos with amazing detail. The 2x optical-quality Telephoto lets you frame the perfect close-up.
NEXT-GENERATION PORTRAITS — Capture portraits with dramatically more detail and color. Just tap to shift the focus between subjects — even after you take the shot.
POWERHOUSE A16 BIONIC CHIP — The superfast chip powers advanced features like computational photography, fluid Dynamic Island transitions, and Voice Isolation for phone calls. And A16 Bionic is incredibly efficient to help deliver great all-day battery life.

list.value:
iPhone 15 – Use & Care Instructions

Charging & Battery Care

Use only Apple-certified (MFi) cables and chargers.

Avoid overcharging; the iPhone 15 supports optimized battery charging.

If the device becomes hot during charging, remove the case and place it in a cool area.

For wireless charging, use Apple’s MagSafe charger or compatible accessories to avoid overheating and magnetic interference.

Temperature & Environment

Recommended operating temperature: 0° to 35°C (32° to 95°F).

Safe storage temperature: -20° to 45°C (-4° to 113°F).

Avoid leaving the device in hot environments like a parked car or direct sunlight.

Water & Dust Resistance

iPhone 15 has an IP68 rating:

Water resistant up to 6 meters for 30 minutes in fresh water.

Not waterproof—avoid submersion in soapy water, seawater, or chlorinated water.

If the device gets wet:

Wipe it gently with a soft, lint-free cloth.

Do not charge the device while it is wet.

Cleaning Your iPhone

Power off and unplug the device before cleaning.

Use a soft, lint-free cloth (microfiber recommended).

You may lightly dampen the cloth with water or 70% isopropyl alcohol if needed.

Do not use bleach, hydrogen peroxide, or abrasive cleaners.

Avoid getting moisture in any openings.

Handling & Protection

Use a protective case and screen protector to prevent physical damage.

Keep the device away from strong magnetic fields and objects that may interfere with MagSafe functionality.

Avoid contact with sharp or abrasive materials that may scratch the surface.

Storage & Backups

Regularly back up your data to iCloud or a computer.

Keep your iPhone updated with the latest iOS version for performance and security enhancements.

Troubleshooting & Maintenance

Restart your iPhone to resolve minor issues.

If problems continue, contact Apple Support for assistance or authorized service.

The iPhone 15 is a solid upgrade. The new design feels sleek and premium, and the performance is noticeably faster thanks to the A16 chip. Battery life is impressive, easily lasting a full day with heavy use. The camera improvements are also great, especially in low light. Definitely worth it if you're coming from an older model.

Battery life is impressive, easily lasting a full day with heavy use. The camera improvements are also great, especially in low light. Definitely worth it if you're coming from an older model.

descriptor.name: Apple iPhone 15 (512 GB) - Yellow
descriptor.short_desc: Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities — so you don’t miss them while you’re doing something else
descriptor.long_desc:
DYNAMIC ISLAND COMES TO IPHONE 15 — Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities — so you don’t miss them while you’re doing something else. You can see who’s calling, track your next ride, check your flight status, and so much more.
INNOVATIVE DESIGN — iPhone 15 features a durable color-infused glass and aluminum design. It’s splash, water, and dust resistant. The Ceramic Shield front is tougher than any smartphone glass. And the 6.1" Super Retina XDR display is up to 2x brighter in the sun compared to iPhone 14.
48MP MAIN CAMERA WITH 2X TELEPHOTO — The 48MP Main camera shoots in super-high resolution. So it’s easier than ever to take standout photos with amazing detail. The 2x optical-quality Telephoto lets you frame the perfect close-up.
NEXT-GENERATION PORTRAITS — Capture portraits with dramatically more detail and color. Just tap to shift the focus between subjects — even after you take the shot.
POWERHOUSE A16 BIONIC CHIP — The superfast chip powers advanced features like computational photography, fluid Dynamic Island transitions, and Voice Isolation for phone calls. And A16 Bionic is incredibly efficient to help deliver great all-day battery life.
